---
title: Tex-Mex Double Tofu Tacos with Avocado Crema and Cheddar Cheese
description: Veggie taco Tuesday? Yes, please! Our protein-packed veggie tacos are loaded with crumbled tofu and tossed in Tex-Mex paste. Juicy tomatoes, velvety avocado crema and salty cheddar cheese complete the tortillas for a taco night you won't soon forget!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tacos-au-tofu-double-facon-tex-mex-a26029a5.jpg
